Package: HOMED
Type: Package
Title: Hierarchically Optimized Methylation Deconvolution
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Yuheng Du
Maintainer: Yuheng Du <yhdu@umich.edu>
Description: HOMED (Hierarchically Optimized Methylation Deconvolution) is a tool that utilizes the hierarchical cell type information to build FACS-based methylation reference panel and estimate cell counts.
Imports: limma, lumi, nlme, genefilter, matrixStats, EpiDISH, doParallel, foreach, parallel, ggplot2, dplyr, RColorBrewer
